comment.body:
Method updates the Property that is represented by this service object.

@param pProperty Object describing the new values to which the Property should be updated. The parameter must not be null and must have a valid ServiceObjectID.
@return Property object describing the updated object in the database. This object is not the same as the one that was passed to the method. The passed Property object should not be used any longer since its data was not updated. The method never returns null.
